-ms-grid-row:1"> <div class="inner clearfix wow" style="animation-delay: 200.0ms;"> <a class="blogImgLink" data-blog-post-alias="week12" dont-color-link="true" href="/week12"> <div class="blogImg" style="background-image: url(https://lirp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/53e775e3/dms3rep/multi/opt/Part+1+%281%29-1920w.png);"><img "="" onerror="handleImageLoadError(this)" src="https://lirp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/53e775e3/dms3rep/multi/opt/Part+1+%281%29-1920w.png"/></div>\n</a>\n<div class="postTextContainer"> <div class="postText clearfix"> <div class="postTitle"> <h3> <a data-blog-post-alias="week12" dont-color-link="true" href="/week12">Exciting Updates From RedFOX Labs - New Miss Universe Philippines Deal, New Advertising Revenue Streams and A Promising Reward Structure</a>\n</h3>\n</div>\n<div class="authorBar"> <span>18 Mar, 2021</span>\n</div>\n<div class="postDescription">RedFOX Labs recently announced its new exclusive three-year content rights provision deal with the well-known Miss Universe Philippines beauty pageant. For the contestants, this partnership means access to a platform to promote their name and brand and build a business from it.                                                                                                            With the rollout of a new streaming platform providing an additional multimedia layer, Ben Fairbank, the founder, and chief executive, states that RedFOX Labs can offer something other than traditional NFT\xe2\x80\x99s like collectibles for these contestants. RedFOX Labs "have some unique ideas on how to make these memorabilia different from the current collectibles in the marketplace."                                                                                                            The streaming platform also provides different ways to monetize advertising. Instead of an intrusive pop-up that takes the stream or users out of the platform, it provides overlays for this very purpose for client content providers.  An e-sport gaming company that wants to do live-streaming will be able to provide, with a one plug button press, the ability "to collect an NFT as a prize or purchase an NFT capturing a moment or an asset" without leaving the stream. On top of that, in the virtual space, they can own billboard and advertising space which they can use to bring in advertising revenue, brand awareness, and utility for the $RFOX token.                                                                                                            As the NFT space pumps and develops rapidly, there is now discussion in the marketplace regarding the "need thoughtfulness" and the general long-term nature of the NFT.  Ben states that there are talks about "IP and the transfer of ownership inside NFTs." The 1155s on the ERC allow you to gather NFTs or tokens inside of NFTs. In simpler terms, within a virtual space, you can sell the virtual merchandise you own as a shop with the inventory inside it or the IP that comes along with that. This is a very unique use case!  Ultimately, Ben thinks it is necessary for "people to know that NFTs are not just a digital picture" but that they can do more now and in the future in the NFT space.                                                                                                            RedFOX Labs is also developing more utility for the $RFOX token, Ben says that $RFOX holders will soon have the opportunity to receive staking rewards.  Additionally, when new information on how the virtual space will work comes to light, he believes that "people are going to see something that is more ahead of what they have potentially anticipated as far as providing value to the $RFOX token and holding it."                                                                                                            There are also mechanisms in the works for making it easier for people to get in and out of positions, and this will address liquidity restrictions for high volume transactions. One of them will involve NFTs when RedFOX Labs rolls out the virtual space \xe2\x80\x93 to be announced. $RFOX holders should also keep a look out for the new liquidity provider promotion to be announced soon, which will include new partnerships and fantastic rewards for those who participate!                                                                                                            $RFOX holders should also be aware that when there is a sale of a large amount of $RFOX tokens, because the market is not very liquid, it can impact price. However, it is vital to understand that with increasing wallet holding numbers and new people entering the ecosystem, other people have been in the ecosystem since the beginning. Naturally, these people would take profit off the table and do these large types of transactions, and it might take a considerable number of wallets to come in and fill the position size left and for people that are starting their journeys.                                                                              Overall, RedFOX Labs is working with centralized exchanges, in addition to the new mechanisms to be introduced in the virtual space and rewards structure which will drive volume and traffic into the token. These new developments will require the possession of $RFOX tokens to participate in the RedFOX Labs ecosystem and ultimately push demand and increase value. There is a deliberate effort by RedFOX Labs to avoid buying fake liquidity and volume and instead provide use cases and utility that brings in real volume, demand, and use.                                                                                                                      And with the virtual space coming out soon, there have been talks of an overarching reward structure for LP pools only. This reward system will reward people for interacting with the platform across the different ventures and allow them to use those rewards in any of the others.                                                                                                            Lastly, although the focus is on creating utility and demand for the $RFOX token to drive volume within the ecosystem, RedFOX Labs expect a new exchanges to come onboard. Ben states that talks are going on between some of them and hopes that the virtual space announcement provides the opportunity to be noticed by the popular tier one exchanges.                                                                                It is an exciting time for the RedFOX Labs ecosystem, especially with the benefits of these new developments and what they mean for long term success. -ms-grid-row:1"> <div class="inner clearfix wow" style="animation-delay: 400.0ms;"> <a class="blogImgLink" data-blog-post-alias="redfox-labs-strikes-exclusive-content-partnership-with-miss-universe-philippines" dont-color-link="true" href="/redfox-labs-strikes-exclusive-content-partnership-with-miss-universe-philippines"> <div class="blogImg" style="background-image: url(https://lirp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/53e775e3/dms3rep/multi/opt/LABS+%281%29-1920w.png);"><img "="" onerror="handleImageLoadError(this)" src="https://lirp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/53e775e3/dms3rep/multi/opt/LABS+%281%29-1920w.png"/></div>\n</a>\n<div class="postTextContainer"> <div class="postText clearfix"> <div class="postTitle"> <h3> <a data-blog-post-alias="redfox-labs-strikes-exclusive-content-partnership-with-miss-universe-philippines" dont-color-link="true" href="/redfox-labs-strikes-exclusive-content-partnership-with-miss-universe-philippines">REDFOX LABS STRIKES EXCLUSIVE CONTENT PARTNERSHIP WITH MISS UNIVERSE PHILIPPINES</a>\n</h3>\n</div>\n<div class="authorBar"> <span>10 Mar, 2021</span>\n</div>\n<div class="postDescription">Ho Chi Minh, Vietnam: 10 March 2021                                              \xe2\x80\x94 Vietnam based RedFOX Labs Joint Stock Company (\xe2\x80\x98                                  RedFOX                                               \xe2\x80\x99) has struck an exclusive deal with the highly popular beauty pageant,                                              Miss Philippines                                               , providing the sole content rights including, video, NFT, photographic and behind the scenes for the next 3 years.                                                                                                                        This deal is a \xe2\x80\x98first-of-its-kind\xe2\x80\x99 and will feed popular media content into the burgeoning ecosystem that RedFOX Labs is building.                                                                                                                           Following the recent acquisition spree including                                              MYMEDIA                                               , one of the larger media players in Southeast Asia and most recently, the                                              Video, Content &amp; Streaming Platform                                  , RedFOX Labs is now on a trajectory to create a superhighway of media content that can be monetized through advertising as well as through the creation of NFTs.                                                                                                                                                  The popularity of the Miss Universe contest in the Philippines can\xe2\x80\x99t be understated. The Philippines have dominated beauty competitions globally for decades and the contest in the Philippines still ranks as one of the most anticipated annually by the 108 Million residents. Beauty pageant contestants and viewers will be able to interact within an ecosystem of RedFOX Labs newest media acquisitions: advertising and its video, content and streaming platform.                                                                                                                                                              And the newly announced                                              NFT Marketplace                                               that RedFOX Labs is building (a Roblox equivalent for the creation and distribution of NFTs), provides a truly world-first opportunity for celebrities and high profile Miss Philippines contestants to link their content to the globally exploding NFT space, introducing new forms of growth revenue streams.                                                                                                                        Ben Fairbank, CEO, and Co-founder of RedFOX Labs commented:                                                                                                                                                           \xe2\x80\x9cThis latest partnership allows us to utilise a number of our ventures at once, to enhance the $RFOX ecosystem growth in Southeast Asia and provide a blueprint for multimedia and NFT deals going forward. We are truly at the cutting edge of this movement and we will showcase many world firsts with this deal.                                                                                                                                     \xe2\x80\x9cAs we have always said, the $RFOX token will have real, tangible, revenue producing value behind it. We are creating real businesses that will thrive in Southeast Asia - all the while, utilizing the $RFOX token as a way to incentivize, trade and create value.                                                                                                                        \xe2\x80\x9cBrian Cu, one of Southeast Asia\xe2\x80\x99s most prolific platform builders who has created some of the biggest startups in the last decade, has joined RedFox Labs and will be focused on building out this exclusive partnership with Miss Philippines.\xe2\x80\x9d                                                                                                            Media contact                                                                                        Ben Fairbank                                                      partnerships                                  @redfoxlabs.io                                                                                                                                                                                                    About RedFOX Labs                                                                                                                                              RedFOX Labs is a venture builder based in Vietnam, that identifies and builds successful business models for the Southeast Asian markets. It is focused on unlocking the true market value of the Southeast Asian digital economy for high consumer demand services such as e-commerce, e-media, e-travel, and esports/gaming and focuses on adding value to the digital economy through the use of emerging technologies such as blockchain. As a company, its value is tradable through its native token (                                  $RFOX                                  ).</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="postArticle" style="-ms-grid-column:3; -ms-grid-row:1"> <div class="inner clearfix wow" style="animation-delay: 600.0ms;"> <a class="blogImgLink" data-blog-post-alias="building-a-rocket-breaking-it-down" dont-color-link="true" href="/building-a-rocket-breaking-it-down"> <div class="blogImg" style="background-image: url(https://lirp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/53e775e3/dms3rep/multi/opt/EwEuFCpXMAISzRx-1920w.jpg);"><img alt="rfox building a rocketship" onerror="handleImageLoadError(this)" src="https://lirp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/53e775e3/dms3rep/multi/opt/EwEuFCpXMAISzRx-1920w.jpg"/></div>\n</a>\n<div class="postTextContainer"> <div class="postText clearfix"> <div class="postTitle"> <h3> <a data-blog-post-alias="building-a-rocket-breaking-it-down" dont-color-link="true" href="/building-a-rocket-breaking-it-down">Building a Rocket \xe2\x80\x93 Breaking it Down!</a>\n</h3>\n</div>\n<div class="authorBar"> <span>09 Mar, 2021</span>\n</div>\n<div class="postDescription">If you\xe2\x80\x99re new to the RedFOX Labs ecosystem, you will more than likely be looking for a simple explanation as to what we are all about, but most importantly, what we are about to do! Let us break it all down for you here of exactly what it takes to be a venture builder and how to build rockets.                                                                                                                                                                                               1. The Premise - Creating a \xe2\x80\x98build-out\xe2\x80\x99 Venture Builder                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    A Venture Builder or                                                                                         startup studios, refer to organisations that systematically build, develop, launch, and scale startups. In short: they generate ideas, explore prototype concepts, and work on \xe2\x80\x9cin-house\xe2\x80\x9d projects to identify new business opportunities that fit into a larger ecosystem!                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    Although this might sound simple, in reality there are enormous challenges, and most don\xe2\x80\x99t succeed! In 2019, the failure rate of startups was around 90%.                                                                                        Find the full research here                                                                                        .                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            So, what\xe2\x80\x99s the formula for success? That\xe2\x80\x99s where our \xe2\x80\x98                                                                                        RFOX 9-point funnel system                                                                                        \xe2\x80\x99                                                                                                                   comes into play. We focus on the fastest 4 growing sectors of the internet economy in Southeast Asia. We ask tough questions and validate our funnel system with data! We assess the opportunity, sector size, number of competitors, show a clear path to profitability with financial targets, resources and technology required, review other successful models and look for improvements that can be made, and whether we can staff these companies with Rockstar talent.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    We DO:                                                                                                                                                        Build companies for RFOX Labs and for the RFOX ecosystem.                                                                                                                                          Employ a D.B.O.T. model (Design, Build, Operate and Transfer).                                                                                                                                          Acquire companies to expedite growth &amp; scale.                                                                                                                                          Launch companies that support an entire ecosystem.                                                                                                                                          Build a modular ecosystem that is powered by and runs on                                                                                                $RFOX                                                                                                .                                                                                                                                                                      Provide tools or platforms for others to build on.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="postArticle" style="-ms-grid-column:4; -ms-grid-row:1"> <div class="inner clearfix wow" style="animation-delay: 800.0ms;"> <a class="blogImgLink" data-blog-post-alias="rfox-eth-pool-round-4-final-snapshot" dont-color-link="true" href="/rfox-eth-pool-round-4-final-snapshot"> <div class="blogImg" style="background-image: url(https://lirp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/53e775e3/dms3rep/multi/opt/REDFOX+LABS+%2821%29-1920w.png);"><img "="" onerror="handleImageLoadError(this)" src="https://lirp-cdn.multiscreensite.com/53e775e3/dms3rep/multi/opt/REDFOX+LABS+%2821%29-1920w.png"/></div>\n</a>\n<div class="postTextContainer"> <div class="postText clearfix"> <div class="postTitle"> <h3> <a data-blog-post-alias="rfox-eth-pool-round-4-final-snapshot" dont-color-link="true" href="/rfox-eth-pool-round-4-final-snapshot">RFOX-ETH Pool ROUND 4  Final Snapshot</a>\n</h3>\n</div>\n<div class="authorBar"> <span>09 Mar, 2021</span>\n</div>\n<div class="postDescription">223 Wallets                                                qualified for LP Extravaganza                                              Round 4! RFOX MEDIA will be a direct avenue for thousands of influencers to market to the Southeast Asian population across digital platforms that will also encompass video streaming.                                                                                                                         The recent                                              acquisition of MYMEDIA Digital                                               will be the first plug-in of RFOX Media - it is a digital marketing platform that connects consumers directly to brands and influencers across food, fashion, sport, and entertainment and its advertisers include global brands such as Samsung, Huawei, Nestle, Lenovo, Grab, Realme, VIVO, and GrandRoyal who market directly to the 35 million users currently engaging in the platform per month.                                                                                                                        Brian Cu, one of Southeast Asia\xe2\x80\x99s most prolific platform builders will assist RedFOX Labs in rolling out the launch of RFOX Media and securing influencers from across the Southeast Asian market to join RFOX Media.                                                                                                                         Cu helped build some of the biggest startups in the last decade. While working as consultant of the Boston Consulting Group, he co-founded Indonesia\'s most popular ride-hailing app Go-Jek. In 2012, he helped build the online fashion store Zalora Philippines. And In 2013, he co-founded Grab Philippines and served as president until August 2020. More recently Brian has founded and launched start-up                                              Byahe                                               to tackle and disrupt the Philippines transport industry.                                                                                                                                     Recently Cu also joined the Board of national airline                                              Cebu Pacific                                               in the Philippines as Non-executive director.                                                                                                                        Ben Fairbank, CEO, and Co-founder of RedFOX Labs commented:                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cLaunching RFOX Media will be a formative piece in our vision. The ability to scale the ventures we are purchasing and plug them into an integrated system, rolling out across Southeast Asia, is what we have been working on relentlessly for two years.                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cWe couldn\xe2\x80\x99t be more delighted to have Brian assist RedFOX Labs to launch and scale RFOX Media. Having worked with Brian previously, we know he understands the RedFOX Labs vision. His expertise in building the biggest platform companies across Southeast Asia and also recruiting mass audiences will ensure the rapid growth we expect for RFOX Media.                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cWe will aim to roll out first in the Philippines and then focus on other key markets such as Indonesia and Vietnam, while still remaining focused on Myanmar where MYMEDIA began and still continues its journey. We have some very exciting and engaging initiatives for RFOX Media and couldn\xe2\x80\x99t be happier with how it is progressing so far.                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cThe Southeast Asian market has 360million internet users, with almost a third - 104million - aged between 25 to 34. They are young, highly platform-literate, and have a thirst for technology and digital inclusion.                                                                                                                         \xe2\x80\x9cThis is who RFOX Media is built for. You can follow                                              RedFOX Labs                                               for further information and details on RFOX Media\xe2\x80\x9d                                                                                                                        Brian Cu commented:                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cHaving watched the RedFOX Labs team working from afar, it is great to see the vision coming together after considerable effort.                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cDigital inclusion is an important topic in Southeast Asia and the media platform RFOX Media are launching, will help people to create, share and monetise their talents.                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cI am happy to help the team realise their goals through the experience I have gained in launching some of the regions biggest companies.\xe2\x80\x9d                                                                                                            ENDS                                                                                                            Media contact                                                      Ben Fairbank                                                      benny@redfoxlabs.io                                                                                                            About RedFOX Labs                                                                                                            RedFOX Labs is a venture builder based in Vietnam, that identifies and builds successful business models for the Southeast Asian markets. As a company, its value is tradable through its native token (                                  $RFOX                                  ).</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="postArticle" style="-ms-grid-column:2; With the recent acquisition of                                                                                                                MYMEDIA Digita                                                                                                                  l, RedFOX Labs has demonstrated an aggressive growth strategy for the region. With additional acquisitions on the horizon and the establishment of ventures                                                                                                                RFOX Games                                                                                                                  and RedFOX Labs Joint Stock Company, the Company is structuring itself for future potential stock exchange listing opportunities.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    NEO Legal specialises in Blockchain and Cryptocurrency law across the globe, as well as being deeply immersed in existing and innovative technology law. The firm offers a number of services spanning from  Initial Coin Offerings (ICO), Decentralized Finance (DeFi),DeFi, structure for start-ups, right through to tokenomics and exchange set-up.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Ben Fairbank, CEO, and Co-founder of RedFOX Labs commented:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cHarly has been with us for approximately one year and knows our project visions intimately. He has been immensely helpful in guiding us through contract negotiations, our token swap and is now architecting our structure as we prepare for potential stock exchange listing opportunities.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      \xe2\x80\x9cWith NEO Legal we have the added benefit of a seasoned legal team that can cover every aspect of a venture builder model. Obviously, the complexities of having one company are challenging enough, but with a venture-model like RedFOX Labs, we needed the very best team to help guide and facilitate our future acquisitions and plans.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    \xe2\x80\x9cWith a current US$180 million market capitalisation, entering the world of acquisitions and potential listing is exciting for our Company and we look forward to working in partnership with Harly and NEO Legal to continue to guide RedFOX Labs\xe2\x80\x99 growth trajectory.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Harly Zappino, Partner at NEO Legal commented:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cWe see exponential growth potential with RedFox Labs as a Company as well as the $RFOX token.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cTheir team is hungry, their work ethic is unprecedented and every team member is high calibre.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cRedFOX Labs pushes innovation boundaries -  -  they are exploring and commercializing sectors that have haven\xe2\x80\x99t even been conceived yet.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cWe are a firm that will remain at the forefront of innovation and technological growth and RedFox Labs is a Company that we absolutely  believe in and are delighted to be working with.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            \xe2\x80\x9cNeo Legal specialises in Blockchain, Corporate and startup. We\xe2\x80\x99re a little different to your traditional Law firm. We take a new, innovative and fast paced approach, where we not only provide legal advice but push the boundaries of our client\xe2\x80\x99s growth.\xe2\x80\x9d                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            ENDS                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            Media contact                                                                                                                              Ben Fairbank                                                                                                                              benny@redfoxlabs.io                                                                                                                              +84 972 980 858                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            About RedFOX Labs                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            RedFOX Labs is a venture builder based in Vietnam, that identifies and builds successful business models for the Southeast Asian markets. It is focused on unlocking the true market value of the Southeast Asian digital economy for high consumer demand services such as e-commerce, e-media, e-travel, and esports/gaming and focuses on adding value to the digital economy by building ad-ons through blockchain. As a company, its value is tradable as the RFOX token, on the Ethereum platform.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="postArticle lastArticle" style="-ms-grid-column:4; -ms-grid-row:2">
